  • Classes in org.modelio.archimate.metamodel.core used by org.modelio.archimate.metamodel.core 
    Class and Description
    ArchimateAbstractElement
    ArchimateAbstractElement vnull This is the inheritance tree root metaclass for Archimate metaclasses : all Archimate metamodel classes inherit directly or indirectly from this metaclass.
    Concept
    Concept vnull All Archimate metamodel elements represented in an Archimate view are Concepts.
    Relationship
    Relationship vnull In addition to the generic elements, the ArchiMate language defines a core set of generic relationships, each of which can connect a predefined set of source and target concepts (in most cases elements, but in a few cases also other relationships).
